   Occidental Petroleum Corp., Los Angeles, confirmed reports
that it has "had an interest" in acquiring European Vinyls
Corp., a jointly owned plastics business of Imperial Chemical
Industries PLC of Britain and Enimont S.p.A. of Italy.
   Occidental Petroleum said that its Occidental Chemical
